### Dodanie interakcji email - poprawne
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/interactions/contacts/adc15ac1-7e05-47c4-9049-c6c89e7b8f9c/email
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-05-17T14:00:00",
  "content": "Wysłano ofertę do klienta",
  "emailAddress": "klient@test.pl",
  "subject": "Oferta współpracy"
}


### Dodanie sms - poprawne
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/interactions/contacts/adc15ac1-7e05-47c4-9049-c6c89e7b8f9c/sms
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-05-17T15:00:00",
  "content": "Wysłano SMS z przypomnieniem",
  "phoneNumber": "+48123456789"
}


### Dodanie spotkania - poprawne
POST {{WebApi_HostAddress}}/api/interactions/contacts/adc15ac1-7e05-47c4-9049-c6c89e7b8f9c/meeting
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "date": "2026-05-18T10:00:00",
  "content": "Spotkanie z klientem",
  "location": "Kraków",
  "durationMinutes": 60
}


